The '''three headed dragon of Jarn''', was a [[dragon]] defeated by [[Arrav]] in the [[Fourth Age]].{{CiteNPC|npc=A R Wright|loc=classicrsw:Transcript:Book_(Shield_of_Arrav){{!}}The Shield of Arrav|quote=Arrav is probably the best known hero of the 4th age. Amoung other achievements he was responsible for stopping the Orcish invasion and defeating the three headed dragon of Jarn.}}

It is unknown whether ''Jarn'' refers to a location, a person, or some other title.

The three headed dragon of Jarn is not considered canon as the only mention of the dragon, in [[Book (Shield of Arrav)|The Shield of Arrav]] book, was removed sometime during ''[[RuneScape Classic]]''<nowiki/>'s lifespan.

==Trivia==
*Jarn was the first three headed dragon mentioned in ''RuneScape'' and predates the addition of the [[King Black Dragon]] by over a year.

